I guess I didn't want you dead.

525
00:30:03,594 --> 00:30:05,470
If you touch my wife again,

526
00:30:05,554 --> 00:30:07,263
I'll kick your ass
out onto the street.

527
00:30:07,347 --> 00:30:08,556
I don't care who you are.

528
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:12,852
I did her a favor. I showed
her her true character.

529
00:30:13,437 --> 00:30:15,313
She's a better person
than you are.

530
00:30:15,397 --> 00:30:18,065
She is too weak to
act on her beliefs.

531
