my own colonel.

533
00:30:26,992 --> 00:30:32,788
All they do is negotiate and
debate and sign treaties.

534
00:30:32,873 --> 00:30:34,499
They are appeasers.

535
00:30:34,583 --> 00:30:39,170
All the while, we are beset by
assassins and traitors, the scum...

536
00:30:39,254 --> 00:30:40,755
Cockroaches?

537
00:30:43,759 --> 00:30:45,635
What are you gonna
do about them?

538
00:30:45,719 --> 00:30:47,720
What is an enemy to you?

539
00:30:48,514 --> 00:30:52,767
Some younger physician
who covets your office?

540
00:30:52,851 --> 00:30:58,356
In my world, there are dangers
and bloodshed and death,

541
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:03,528
and that makes you a man.
