know what you're planning to do.

546
00:31:17,292 --> 00:31:20,795
Whatever it takes to
protect my country.

547
00:31:31,974 --> 00:31:33,724
You broke into his apartment?

548
00:31:33,809 --> 00:31:35,560
I didn't break in.

549
00:31:37,145 --> 00:31:38,896
I wish I believed you.

550
00:31:38,981 --> 00:31:40,565
I can fix this.

551
00:31:40,649 --> 00:31:42,275
I already did.

552
00:31:43,318 --> 00:31:45,736
He was gonna press charges,

553
00:31:45,821 --> 00:31:48,447
but I promised him you'd leave.

554
00:31:50,951 --> 00:31:52,994
You're kicking me out?

555
00:31:53,078 --> 00:31:55,079
I'll explain it
to your psychiatrist,

556
00:31:55,163 --> 00:31:58,833
but, yeah, you gotta
go somewhere else.

557
00:32:01,378 --> 00:32:03,421
House, I know
when things go wrong,

558
00:32:03,505 --> 00:32:05,715
usually you just double down
and get more involved.

559
00:32:05,799 --> 00:32:09,093
But here, you could go to jail.

560
00:32:09,177 --> 00:32:11,887
And I truly believe

561
00:32:11,972 --> 00:32:14,432
