his life in our hands.

677
00:39:47,719 --> 00:39:49,803
All the good we've done,

678
00:39:51,014 --> 00:39:55,184
every life we've saved,
it would have meant nothing

679
00:39:55,268 --> 00:39:59,063
if we just sent him off to kill
hundreds of thousands of people.

680
00:39:59,147 --> 00:40:00,731
Look at the news.

681
00:40:01,441 --> 00:40:03,108
The moderates are taking over.

682
00:40:03,193 --> 00:40:05,527
There's hope for peace talks.

683
00:40:06,863 --> 00:40:09,782
You tell the world
that I faked this test,

684
00:40:10,325 --> 00:40:14,578
Dibala becomes a martyr.
The massacres begin.

685
00:40:14,954 --> 00:40:17,956
I cover this up,
I become your accomplice.

686
00:40:19,042 --> 00:40:21,668
You think you can
guilt me into that?

687
00:40:27,092 --> 00:40:29,676
If the cops are
going to come for me,

688
00:40:30,095 --> 00:40:31,678
please warn me

689
00:40:32,889 --> 00:40:35,349
so that I can
tell my wife first.

690
00:40:44,192 --> 00:40:45,526
Chase,

691
00:40:46,820 --> 00:40:49,071
you really think you can
kill another human being

692
00:40:49,155 --> 00:40:51,740
