696
00:41:13,638 --> 00:41:15,305
That's nice.

697
00:41:15,390 --> 00:41:18,976
Even nicer, he's approving
the garden expansion.

698
00:41:19,269 --> 00:41:20,394
Huh.

699
00:41:20,937 --> 00:41:23,063
And even more nicer,

700
00:41:23,148 --> 00:41:25,566
